author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Nooky Jones, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited the The Current studio back in 2017.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Hello
00:06:17 How Come You Don’t Call Me Anymore?
00:11:35 Bad Girl

Musicians
Cameron Kinghorn – vocals
Reid Kenedy – drums
Adam Meckler – trumpet 
Scott Agster – trombone
Kevin Gastonguay – keyboard
Andrew Foreman – bass

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark
Producer – Andrea Swensson
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
